\id COL - Zanaki Colossians
\h Abhakorosai
\toc3 Abhakorosai
\toc2 Abhakorosai
\toc1 Enyaarubha ya Pauro ku Bhakorosai
\mt2 Enyaarubha ya Pauro ku
\mt1 Bhakorosai
\imt1 Obhutaangiro
\ip Enyaarubha yino ekaamirwe na Pauro, omweega wa Yeesu Krisito, ku Bhakrisito bho omugye gwa Korosai. Korosai gwaari omugye musuuhu mukyaaro kya Asia (niyo Obhuturuki ya bhoono).
\ip Pauro yakaamiri enyaarubha yino eriibhaga yaari mukibhoho. Ataagiiri Korosai omweene, nawe akiigwa kubha abheegya bho orurimi bhaari bharanyaakya Abhakrisito eyo. Abhakrisito bha Korosai harya bhaari amahizo abhiri, Abhakrisito bhe Ekiyahudi na bhe Ekiyunaani.
\ip Abhaatu bhe Ekiyahudi bhano bheegirye ameegyo go orurimi, bhaari bhareegya kubha eraabhe omuutu yaari omwaanamweega wa Yeesu, ataanagirye okwiikiriribhwa na Taatabhugya eraabhe ataasaarirwe no okutuniirira emigiro ne eziinyaangi zye Ekiyahudi. Abhaatu bhe Ekiyunaani bhano bheegirye ameegyo go orurimi, bhaari bhareegya kubha, kwe ekigirirye bhakarora kubha omubhiri gune ebhibhi na Taatabhugya atana ebhibhi, etaari kuturikana Yeesu abhe Taatabhugya na yiikare mukyaaro kyo omuutu.
\ip Pauro arakyoora iguru wa ameegyo gayo go orurimi kwo okugaamba obhuheene kwiiguru wa Yeesu. Yeesu Krisito ni Taatabhugya, ari iguru we ebhigiro bhyoosi mukyaaro na mwiisaaro. Akiikara mukyaaro, yaari muutu, na akakwa kwiiguru ye ebhibhi bhyeetu okubha twaabhirwe. Omuutu araamwiikirirye Yeesu, bhutariho obhweendi bhwo okutuniirira eziinyaangi zyozyoosi.
\ip Pauro arabhabhuurira Abhakrisito kubha, ereenderwa bhatige eteemo embiihu ye ekare, no okutaanga kubha no obhwiikari obhuhya bhuno bhukumuzomera Taatabhugya.
\c 1
\s1 Obhukeerya
\p 
\v 1 Enyaarubha yino nikaamiri enye Pauro, nikabhirikirwa kubha omweega wa Krisito Yeesu kwo obhuseegi bhwa Taatabhugya, niari hamwe na Timoteo, omwiikirirya omurikyeetu.
\v 2 Turabhakaamira emwe abhahoreeru\f + \fr 1:2 \fk Abhahoreeru\ft . Rora engʼana yino mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* bhano mukwiikara mumugye gwa Korosai, emwe abhaheene abharikyeetu kwo okugwaatana na Krisito.
\p Orubhaango no omureembe okurwa ku Taatabhugya Taata weetu, bhibhe neemwe.
\s1 Amasabhi no okumubhuurira Taatabhugya “Ozomirye”
\p 
\v 3 Kyoomeera turamubhuurira Taatabhugya, “Ozomirye, Taata wo Omukuru weetu Yeesu Krisito,” hano tukubhasabhira emwe.
\v 4 Turakora ego, kwo okubha twiigwiiri kyeego mukumwiikirirya Krisito Yeesu, no okubhaseega abhahoreeru bhoosi.
\v 5 Obhwiikirirya bhweenyu no obhuseegi bhweenyu bhuratuukana ne eriisigo ryeenyu kubha, murasuungʼaana orubhaango runo Taatabhugya abhatuuriiri mwiisaaro. Mumariri kwiigwa iguru ye eriisigo riyo hano mwarwaaziirwe amangʼana go obhuheene, nago nigo Amangʼana Amazomu.
\v 6 Amangʼana Amazomu gayo gaahikiri kweemwe, bhoono garanyaragana mukyaaro kyoosi. Garageenderera kugirya abhaatu bhamukyoorere Taatabhugya, kyeego ekatuukira kweemwe kweema orusiku runo mwiigwiiri iguru yo orubhaango rwa Taatabhugya, no okumenya obhuheene iguru yo orubhaango rwaaye.
\v 7 Emwe mukeega Amangʼana Amazomu gayo okurwa ku Epafura, omurikyeetu omuseegwa. Ewe ni muhokya omuheene wa Krisito kwiiguru weenyu.
\v 8 Woosi atubhuuriiri iguru yo obhuseegi bhweenyu bhuno bhukutuukana ne Ekoro Muhoreeru.\f + \fr 1:8 \fk Ekoro Muhoreeru\ft . Rora amangʼana gano mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f*
\p 
\v 9 Kwe ekigirirye kiyo, tukyaari kutiga kubhasabhira, kweema orusiku runo tukiigwa amangʼana geenyu. Turasabha Taatabhugya abhahe amangʼeeni goosi kugano ewe akweenda. Na kuriyo, abhahe amangʼeeni goosi no obhumenyi bhuno bhukurwa kwe Ekoro Muhoreeru.
\v 10 Niho muraanagye kwiikara kyeego Omukuru Yeesu akweenda, no okumuzomeerya mumangʼana goosi. Obhwiikari bhweenyu bhuramuzomera kwe emirimo gyeenyu emizomu, kweeki murakiraho okumumenya Taatabhugya.
\v 11 Kweeki turasabha Taatabhugya abhe arabhagumirya kwo obhuturo bhwaaye obhukuru, okubha munagye kukongʼera. Ambe, mubhe no obhuzomererwa kugoosi
\v 12 mukubhuga, “Ozomirye, Taata Taatabhugya,” kwo okubha abhasakiirye okungʼarira kusuungʼaana engabho ya abhahoreeru bhano abhatuuriiri mubhutemi bhwo obhweero.
\v 13 Atutuurirye okurwa mubhutemi bhwe ekiirima, atusaamirye no okutusikirya mubhutemi bhwo Omwaana waaye\f + \fr 1:13 \fk Omwaana waaye\ft . Rora \ft \it Omwaana wa Taatabhugya\it* mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* omuseegwa.
\v 14 Kwo okuhitira Omwaana waaye tutuuriibhwe, kwo okubha ebhibhi bhyeetu bhyaabhiirwe.
\s1 Omwaana wa Taatabhugya ano obhuturo iguru wa bhyoosi
\q1 
\v 15 Omwaana wa Taatabhugya niwe ekireengyo kyeego Taatabhugya ari,
\q1 yiingabha Taatabhugya omweene atakurorekana.
\q1 Ewe niwe omukuru wo obhuturo iguru ye ebhigiro bhyoosi,
\q1 
\v 16 kwo okubha kwo okuhitira kweewe, ebhigiro bhyoosi bhyaateemirwe,
\q1 bhino bhiri mwiisaaro na bhino bhiri mukyaaro,
\q1 bhino bhikurorekana na bhino bhitakurorekana,
\q1 bho obhunagya kasi abhatemi, abhakuru kasi // bha amanaga.
\q1 Bhyoosi bhyaateemirwe kwo okuhitira ewe na kwiiguru waaye.
\q1 
\v 17 Ewe yaari ariho bhikyaari kubhaho ebhigiro bhyoosi okuteemwa,
\q1 na aragirya ebhigiro bhyoosi bhihaagwaatana hamwe.
\q1 
\v 18 Ewe niwe omutwe gwo omubhiri, no omubhiri nigwe ekanisa.
\q1 Ewe niwe obhweemero,
\q1 kweeki, yaari omutaangi okuryooka okurwa mubhaku,
\q1 okubha abhe omukuru iguru we ebhigiro bhyoosi.
\q1 
\v 19 Niigo, kwo okubha ekazomera Taatabhugya kubha,
\q1 obhukuunaanio bhwaaye bhwoosi bhuri muusi wo Omwaana waaye.
\q1 
\v 20 Kweeki, ekamuzomera Taatabhugya kubha,
\q1 yiigwaanie ebhigiro bhyoosi neewe kwo okuhitira Omwaana waaye,
\q1 ebhigiro bhino bhiri mukyaaro muno na bhino bhiri mwiisaaro.
\q1 Akakora ego kwo okureeta omureembe,
\q1 okuhitira amanyiinga go Omwaana waaye gano gakiitika kumusaraba.
\p 
\v 21 Inyuma hayo, neemwe mwaari kure na Taatabhugya. Mwaari abhabhisa bhaaye, mumiiseego geenyu, gano gaagirirye eziiteemwa zyeenyu eziimbiihu. Nawe bhoono Taatabhugya abhiigwaanirye neewe,
\v 22 kwe enzira yo oruku rwo omubhiri gwa Krisito. Akakora ego okubha abhareete embere waaye murabha abhahoreeru, mutana isarya naabhe amasoro.
\v 23 Nawe mureenderwa okugeenderera kwiikirirya Amangʼana Amazomu, mukubha bhagumiru no okubha na amanaga. Mutangʼeenwa na abhaandi okutiga eriisigo rino mukabhona hano mukiigwa Amangʼana Amazomu. Amangʼana gayo Amazomu garwaazirwe kubhaatu bhoosi bha mukyaaro hano, na neenye Pauro nibheeri omuhokya waaye.
\s1 Emirimo gya Pauro mumakanisa
\p 
\v 24 Bhoono nirazomererwa enyaako yino nikubhona kwiiguru weenyu. Mumubhiri gwaane niragwaatana ne enyaako ya Krisito kwiiguru yo omubhiri gwaaye, nigwe ekanisa.
\v 25 Taatabhugya anituuriri enye kubha omuhokya we ekanisa yaaye, okubha nibharwaazire emwe engʼana yaaye yoosi kyeego eri,
\v 26 nikyo okugaamba, embiso yaaye yino yabhisirwe kweema ekare kurwiibhuro rwoosi. Nawe bhoono Taatabhugya ayikuundukuriiri abhahoreeru bhaaye.\f + \fr 1:26 \xt Rora Abhaefeso 3:3-6.\xt*\f*
\v 27 Taatabhugya akaseega okubhakuundukurira obhuzomu bhwe embiso yo okuruguurya no obhuguungo kubhaatu bhano bhatari Abhayahudi. Embiso yiyo ni Krisito ari muusi weenyu, ewe niwe eriisigo ryeetu kubha tusikire mubhuguungo bhwa Taatabhugya.
\p 
\v 28 Krisito niwe wuno tukumurwaaza hano tukurekya no okweegya abhaatu bhoosi kwa amangʼeeni goosi. Kweego turamurwaaza ewe, okubha tureete bhoosi embere wa Taatabhugya, bhagumiiri kutuukana no okugwaatana kwaabhu na Krisito.
\v 29 Ni kwe ekigirirye kiyo nirabha no omukya kuhizana ne emirimo kwo okuhokeerya amanaga maaru gano Krisito akuuniha.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Ndeenda mumenye kyeego nikuhizana ne emirimo kwiiguru weenyu, na kubhaatu bha mumugye gwa Raodikia bhano bhakyaari kunirora, na kwiiguru ya abhaandi bhoosi bhano bhakyaari kunirora enye.
\v 2 Nirakora ego okubha mutoongerwe ekoro no okugwaatanibhwa mubhuseegi, na mwiizuribhwe obhuheene bhwaaru mumangʼeeni goosi gano gakubhaha obhuheene. Niho muramenya embiso ya Taatabhugya, nayo ni kumumenya Krisito omweene.
\v 3 Muusi waaye nimwe ziibhisiri eziihata zyoosi zya amangʼeeni no obhumenyi.
\p 
\v 4 Nirabhakaamira gayo, okubha mutiikirirya okungʼeenwa no omuutu wowoosi kumangʼana go orurimi, naabhe kwa amangʼana go okusaambaarukya bhukongʼu.
\v 5 Niragaamba ego, kwe ekigirirye kyo okubha hamwe neemwe mukoro, yiingabha nitari hamwe neemwe kwo omubhiri. Nirazomererwa kwo okubha niriigwa iguru yo obhumwe bhweenyu no obhukongʼeru bhwo obhwiikirirya bhweenyu ku Krisito.
\s1 Obhwiikari obhuhya bhwe Ekikrisito
\p 
\v 6 Ambe bhoono, kwo okubha mumwiikiriirye Krisito Yeesu kubha ni Mukuru, mugeenderere kwiikara kwo okugwaatana neewe.
\v 7 Kweego, emiri gyeenyu gibhe muusi waaye, na mwoomboke obhuhoru bhweenyu iguru waaye, eno mukukongʼera mubhwiikirirya kyeego mukeegibhwa. Kweeki mubhe abhaatu bhano bhakubhuga, “Ozomirye, Taatabhugya,” eriibhaga ryoosi.
\p 
\v 8 Mwiiriihe mutaaza kukaangiribhwa kwa ameegyo ga bhusa na go orurimi gano gakutuukana ne eziinyaangi zya abhaatu. Ameegyo gayo gariisigira eziikoro zino zirabhaaha ekyaaro kino\f + \fr 2:8 \fk Eziikoro zino zirabhaaha ekyaaro kino\ft , obhugazuro obhuundi bhuratura kubha, \fqa ameegyo ge ekyaaro kino.\f* na ameegyo gayo gatari ga Krisito,
\v 9 kwo okubha obhukuunaanio bhwoosi bhwa Taatabhugya bhuri muusi wo omubhiri gwa Krisito.
\v 10 Neemwe muheerwe obhukuunaanio bhwoosi bhwo okugwaatana na Krisito. Ewe niwe Omukuru iguru wa bho obhunagya na abhatemi bhoosi mukyaaro kino kitakurorekana.
\v 11 Eriibhaga mwagwaateeni na Krisito, mukasaarwa\f + \fr 2:11 \fk Mukasaarwa\ft . Rora \ft \it okusaarwa\it* mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* kwe esaaro yino etakukorwa kwa amabhoko ga abhaatu, nawe kwe enzira ya Krisito, okubha aruusye omubhiri gwe ebhibhi.
\v 12 Eriibhaga mwabatiizirwe, mukakwa no okubhiikwa hamwe na Krisito, kweeki mukaryooka hamwe neewe, kwo okubha mukiikirirya eziinguru zya Taatabhugya wuno yamuryooriri okurwa mubhaku.
\p 
\v 13 Neemwe mwaari abhaku kwe ekigirirye kye ebhibhi bhyeenyu, kweeki mutasaarirwe omutima gweenyu gwe ebhibhi. Nawe Taatabhugya abhaheeri obhuhoru hamwe na Krisito na atwaabhiiri ebhibhi bhyeetu bhyoosi.
\v 14 Hano Yeesu yanyaakiibhwe kumusaraba, amakaamo ge emigiro gano gakatutinira ekiina, gakanyaakibhwa hamwe neewe, nikyo tukugaamba eriibhaga riyo Taatabhugya akayiruusya esiiri yeetu ye ebhibhi.
\v 15 Kweego Taatabhugya akabharuusya abhatemi bhoosi obhunagya mukyaaro kino kitakurorekana, akabhahiza kimwe.
\p 
\v 16 Ambe, omuutu wowoosi atabhatinira ekiina kwo okubha murarya ebhyaakurya ne ebhinyweebhwa bhino bhakubhuga migiro, kasi kwo okubha mutakutuniirira Enyaangi yo Okuhiita, kasi enyaangi yo okutaazwa omweeri, kasi orusiku rwo okumuunya.\f + \fr 2:16 \fk Orusiku rwo okumuunya\ft . Rora amangʼana gano mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f*
\v 17 Gayo goosi ni kizuruuru kya amangʼana gano Abhayahudi bhaari bhariiseegera kubha garaaza. Nawe amangʼana ageene gari ku Krisito omweene.
\v 18 Bhariho abhaatu bhano bhakukumiirirya bhukongʼu amangʼana go obhusuuku bhwi igutu na go okuseengera bhamaraika.\f + \fr 2:18 \fk Bhamaraika\ft . Rora engʼana \ft \it maraika\it* mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* Mutabhiikirirya bhataaza bhakabharuusya esaambo yeenyu ya kirakeego. Abhaatu bhayo bhariizuungya, kwo okubha bharabhuga bharuuzi amangʼana gayo mubhurori. Nawe kwe eheene, bhatuumbaahiri kwa amiiseego gaabhu mabhiihu ge ekyaaro.
\v 19 Abhaatu bhayo, bhiiyaahwiiri na Krisito wuno akukaangata ekanisa, araabhe omutwe gwo omubhiri gwaaye. Krisito niwe arariisya no okugwaatania hamwe ebhiimo ne emigiha gyoosi. Kweego, omubhiri gwaaye gwoosi gurakiina bhuzomu kyeego Taatabhugya akweenda.
\p 
\v 20 Emwe, mukakwa hamwe na Krisito, na kweego akabhatuurya okurwa mubhubhaahi bhwe eziikoro zino zikubhaaha ekyaaro kino.\f + \fr 2:20 \fk Eziikoro zino zikubhaaha ekyaaro kino\ft , obhugazuro obhuundi bhuratura kubha, \fqa ameegyo ge ekyaaro kino.\f* Ambe, ni kwaki muriikara kyeego abhaatu bha mukyaaro muno? Mutiikirirya okwiigwa obhuswaagyo kya bhuno,
\v 21 “Mutagwaata kino! Mutakunia kirya! Mutasama kiyo!”
\v 22 Gayo goosi ni iguru we ebhigiro bhino bhikusarika kwiibhaga iguhi okumara okuhokeeribhwa, eheene ni migiro na ameegyo ga abhaatu abheene.
\v 23 Ni heene, bhano bhakutuniirira obhuswaagyo bhuyo bhararorekana kubha bhana amangʼeeni. Bharatuniirira obhusabhi bhuno bhiituuriiri abheene, obhusuuku bhwiigutu no okubhaaha emibhiri gyaabhu kwo obhuhaari. Nawe obhuswaagyo bhuyo bhutakutura kuribhira enaamba embiihu yo omubhiri.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Bhoono, kwo okubha muryookiri hamwe na Krisito, mukomye amangʼana ga mwiisaaro, eno Krisito yiikeeri orubhaara rwo obhuryo rwa Taatabhugya.
\v 2 Mwiiseege amangʼana gano gari mwiisaaro, mutiiseega ga mukyaaro muno,
\v 3 kwo okubha mukuuri hamwe na Krisito. Bhoono muriikara hamwe na Krisito embere wa Taatabhugya. Nawe obhwiikari bhuyo hamwe neewe bhutakurorekana kubhaatu abhaandi.
\v 4 Kweego, obhuhoru bhweenyu bhuratuukana na Krisito. Eriibhaga rino araarorekane, niho neemwe muraarorekane hamwe neewe no okugwaatana mubhuguungo bhwaaye.
\p 
\v 5 Ambe bhoono, mutaase kure amangʼana goosi ga mukyaaro kino gano gari muusi weenyu, nago ni bhuseebheeti, amakire, enaamba embiihu, amiiseego mabhiihu ne enaamba ye ebhigiro. Kubha ne enaamba ye ebhigiro ni kisi no okuseengera emisaambwa, okutiga kumuseengera Taatabhugya.
\v 6 Amangʼana kya gayo, nigo gakukora Taatabhugya atiindire abhaatu bhano bhatakumwiigwa.\f + \fr 3:6 \ft Amakaamo agaandi ge Ekiyunaani gatana amangʼana \fqa abhaatu bhano bhatakumwiigwa. \xt Rora Abhaefeso 5:6.\xt*\f*
\v 7 Hano mwaari muragwaatana na abhaatu kya bhayo, neemwe mwaari muriikara kuriingʼaana na amangʼana gayo amabhiihu.
\v 8 Nawe bhoono, mutige bhukongʼu amangʼana goosi gayo, kyeego obhuhaari, obhururu, obhubhi, amatuki na amangʼana amabhi ge eziisoni gano gatakweenderwa muminwa gyeenyu.
\v 9 Mutabhuurirana orurimi, kwo okubha muruusirye eziiteemo zyeenyu zye ekare hamwe na amahokya gaaye,
\v 10 na mwiibhohiri omutima omuhya. Taatabhugya omweene akateema omutima omuhya, na arageenderera kugukora gutuubhane bhukongʼu neewe, okubha munagye okumumenya bhuzomu.
\v 11 Kweego, bhutariho obhwaahuri gati yo Omuyahudi na wuno atari Omuyahudi, wuno asaarirwe na wuno atasaarirwe, omuutu wuno akurweera ekyaaro kya kure naabhe abhe omutuumbaahu, abhe omugya kasi wuno atari mwiiragaanzi. Nawe Krisito niwe omurito, na neewe ari muusi wa bhoosi.
\p 
\v 12 Bhoono, kwo okubha emwe mubheeri abhasorwa bha Taatabhugya, na abhahoreeru abhaseegwa, mubhe bhe ebhigoongi, abhazomu, abhasuuku, abhanyoohu na abhiikongʼeererya.
\v 13 Kweego mwiigumiirirye ne eraabhe owumwe weenyu ane engʼana kumurikyaaye, mwaabhirane kyeego Omukuru yabhaabhiiri emwe.
\v 14 Kukira gayo goosi mwiiseege, kwo okubha obhuseegi nibhwo bhurabhagwaatania bhoosi mubhumwe bhuno bhukuunaaniri.
\v 15 Omureembe gwa Krisito gubhaahe muziikoro zyeenyu. Emwe mubheeri omubhiri gumwe, kweego mubhirikiirwe kwiikara kwo omureembe. Kweeki mubhe murabhuga, “Ozomirye, Taatabhugya.”
\v 16 Engʼana ya Krisito yiikare kwo obhwaaru muusi weenyu, eno muriiyeegya no okurekyana no okwiikyoora kwa amangʼeeni goosi. Mumweembere Taatabhugya kwe eziikoro zyeenyu no okubhuga, “Ozomirye,” kwe ezaburi na ameembo go okumukumya Taatabhugya.
\p 
\v 17 Gogoosi gano mukugaamba kasi kukora, mukore kuriina ryo Omukuru Yeesu, mukubhuga, “Ozomirye, Taata Taatabhugya,” kuhitira kweewe.
\s1 Obhwiikari obhuzomu muziinyuumba zya Abhakrisito
\p 
\v 18 Emwe abhakari, mubhe murabhiigwa abhasubhe bheenyu, kyeego ekweenderwa kubhaatu bhano bhakumwiigwa Omukuru Yeesu.
\v 19 Neemwe abhasubhe, mubhe muraseega abhakari bheenyu, mutabha bhahaari kweebho.
\v 20 Neemwe abhaana, mubhe murabhiigwa abhiibhuri bheenyu mugoosi, kwo okubha okukora ego kuramuzomera Omukuru Yeesu.
\v 21 Neemwe bhataata, mutabhazabhura abhaana bheenyu, okubha bhataaza bhakakwa emitwe.
\v 22 Neemwe abhagya, mubhiigwe abhakuru bheenyu bha mukyaaro hano kwe emirimo gyoosi. Mutakora ego hano bhakubharora ego okubha mwiiyeerekye kubha mureenderwa, nawe mubhasuuke eriibhaga ryoosi kwo obhuheene bhwe ekoro, kwo okubha muramusuuka Omukuru Yeesu.
\v 23 Ryoryoosi rino mukukora, mukore kwe ekoro yimwe, kwe ekigirirye kyo Omukuru, ne etari iguru ya abhaatu.
\v 24 Muhiite kubha Omukuru wuno mukumuhokeerya niwe Krisito, na niwe akubhaha engabho yino abharagiiri.
\v 25 Nawe wowoosi wuno akukora amabhi arasuungʼaana kuriingʼaana no obhubhi bhwaaye, kwo okubha Omukuru atana bhwaahuri.
\c 4
\nb 
\v 1 Neemwe abhakuru, mubhe murabhakorera abhagya bheenyu kwe eheene na kyeego ekweenderwa. Muhiite kubha neemwe mwoosi munawe Omukuru mwiisaaro.
\s1 Obhuswaagyo na amasabhi ga Pauro
\p 
\v 2 Mubhe murasabha eziisiku zyoosi, murateengeeza no okumubhuurira Taatabhugya, “Ozomirye.”
\v 3 Mutusabhire na neetwe okubha Taatabhugya atwiigurire enzira yo okurwaaza engʼana yaaye iguru wa Krisito, yino ekare yaraarikiri embiso yaaye. Na neenye nibhohirwe kwiiguru yo okurwaaza amangʼana gayo.
\v 4 Kweego, mubhe murasabha Taatabhugya kubha, nibhe na amanaga go okurwaaza kubhweero amangʼana gayo kyeego nikweenderwa kugaamba.
\p 
\v 5 Mubhe na amangʼeeni mubhwiigwaani bhweenyu na bhano bhatakumwiikirirya Omukuru Yeesu. Mutabhurya eriibhaga.
\v 6 Amangʼana geenyu gabhe mazomu na go okusakirya, okubha mumenye kyeego mukweenderwa kukyoora abhaatu bhoosi bhuzomu.
\s1 Amangʼana go okuraga
\p 
\v 7 Omwiikirirya omurikyeetu omuseegwa Tikiko ni muhokya omuheene. Turakora emirimo gyo Omukuru Yeesu kwa hamwe. Ewe arabhabhuurira amangʼana gaane goosi.
\v 8 Nimutumiri kweemwe okubha abhaganire amangʼana geetu no okubhatoongera eziikoro zyeenyu.
\v 9 Araaza hamwe na Onesimo, omwiikirirya omurikyeetu. Ewe niwe omuutu wo oweenyu no omuseegwa omuheene. Bharabhabhuurira amangʼana goosi gano gakukorwa oweetu hano.
\p 
\v 10 Aristariko, wuno abhohirwe hamwe na neenye mukibhoho hano, arabhakeerya. Mariko, wamwaabhu Barinaaba, arabhakeerya. Mumariri kusuungʼaana amaragiriryo iguru waaye. Hano araahike kweemwe, mumusuungʼaane bhuzomu.
\v 11 Yeesu neewe, wuno akubhirikirwa Yusito, arabhakeerya. Gati wa Abhayahudi bhano bhiikiriirye Krisito, bhano ego nibho bhakukora emirimo kubhutemi bhwa Taatabhugya hamwe na neenye, nabho bhanitoongeeri ekoro bhukongʼu.
\v 12 Epafura, omugya wa Krisito Yeesu no omuutu wo oweenyu, arabhakeerya. Eriibhaga ryoosi arakora omukya kubhasabhira emwe kubha mugumire mubhwiikirirya bhweenyu no okukongʼa, mukubha no obhukaari kugoosi gano Taatabhugya akweenda.
\v 13 Ndamumenyeekererya kubha, arakora emirimo kwo omukya kwiiguru weenyu na kubhaatu bhe emigye gya Raodikia na Hierapori.
\v 14 Omugabhu weetu omuseegwa Ruuka na Dema, bharabhakeerya.
\v 15 Emwe, mubhakeerye abhiikirirya abharikyeetu bha Raodikia. Kweeki mumukeerye Nimufa, na abhaatu bhe ekanisa bhano bhakusikanira munyuumba yaaye.
\p 
\v 16 Hano mukumara okusoma enyaarubha yino kweemwe, muyihikye kubhiikirirya bhe ekanisa ya Raodikia okubha bhayo nabho bhayisome. Neemwe mukomye enzira yo okubhona enyaarubha yino nikabhatumira ebho muyisome.
\v 17 Mumubhuurire Arikipo kubha, amare bhuzomu emirimo gino Omukuru amuheeri.
\p 
\v 18 Enye Pauro nirakaama obhukeerya bhuno kwo okubhoko kwaane omweene. Muhiite kubha niri mukibhoho. Orubhaango rwa Taatabhugya rubhe hamwe neemwe.
